    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基本玩法</h2>“一片祥和”的空间站上，大批失控的机器人会主动攻击正常的机体。你将控制新型E-201，利用自身特性、收集强力技能、合理搭配道具，从而组合出强力Combo,击败各种各样的敌人。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/47d21a3ce0c499b9f1f08a41aed81868.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/47d21a3ce0c499b9f1f08a41aed81868.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/47d21a3ce0c499b9f1f08a41aed81868.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >技能消耗</h2>主角可以储存燃料、氢能、电能三种能源。主动释放技能需要消耗能源，不同技能消耗能源有所不同。合理搭配装备、规划好能源使用才能最大化输出。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/da1b56269a6c088f011fbf9ddb499a89.webp?t=1771333242\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/da1b56269a6c088f011fbf9ddb499a89.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" class=\"bb_img\" width=720 height=320 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >连携效果</h2>技能和道具之间有羁绊属性，筹齐相应数量可激活对应的连携效果。连携效果对角色有不俗的提升，往往能够在战斗的关键时刻反败为胜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/80abb4861c45d948229cf6c8b1668179.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/80abb4861c45d948229cf6c8b1668179.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >选择奖励</h2>发扬肉鸽游戏的传统艺能，冒险过程中玩家可根据需要选择下一关的奖励：晶石（准备买买买）、芯片（收集和升级主动技能）、装备（获得被动技能）。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/a6b9570b3d4bf561bf1ebaea5ba00ea0.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/a6b9570b3d4bf561bf1ebaea5ba00ea0.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/a6b9570b3d4bf561bf1ebaea5ba00ea0.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人种类和特性</h2>闯关路上各式各样的失控机器人会攻击你，他们的攻击方式和特性各不相同。熟悉他们的行为模式更有利于你击败他们。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/1390bb4cea0bf8f1028206680075c23f.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/1390bb4cea0bf8f1028206680075c23f.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/1390bb4cea0bf8f1028206680075c23f.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机关挑战</h2>横板游戏的机关陷阱从来不会缺席。本作的机关挑战设置了丰厚的奖励，风险越高回报越大，对自己操作有信心的朋友千万不要错过。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/e469818dcd12ff682b5af2f1fbf5868a.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/e469818dcd12ff682b5af2f1fbf5868a.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/e469818dcd12ff682b5af2f1fbf5868a.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强大boss</h2>每一大关总有一位守门员，他们拥有特别强大的技能和属性，若未能合理地运用自身的技能组合，大概率会被它送回去，回炉重做！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/c41d41966b3f9400e08c39878fc3469e.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/c41d41966b3f9400e08c39878fc3469e.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/c41d41966b3f9400e08c39878fc3469e.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >银河竞速</h2>在紧张刺激宇宙冒险中不妨来一场速度与激情的竞速比拼。赢得锦标赛能解锁更多丰厚奖励。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/235d21ad6504416f7626c9ffd00af3bc.poster.avif?t=1771333242\" width=720 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/235d21ad6504416f7626c9ffd00af3bc.webm?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2289550/extras/235d21ad6504416f7626c9ffd00af3bc.mp4?t=1771333242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>BUG反馈及玩法交流<br>玩家QQ群：223489649<br>B站：<br>Discord: <br>Twitter:Hang John",
